Author: Rohan Tabish
Organization: University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign, IL, USA


This is a simple FFT benchmark. 

driver.c: This file has main function.
fft.c: This file has the actual fft function. The #define NUM_POINTS defines number of points that for which we want FFT 
Makefile: This file is used to compile the code. 

How to run:
./fft

